{"tid":780553,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"畢菲特、索羅斯齊增持蘋果 巴郡持倉470億美元","createTime":"2018-08-15T08:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T08:47:10.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6866b530f8cf4541d38608f13d0297f753708483","tid":780553,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"股神畢菲特（Warren Buffett）投資旗艦巴郡公佈調整1,800億美元的股票投資組合，該公司在今年二季度增持5%蘋果公司股份，持倉由2.396億股增至2.52億。蘋果市值上周突破1萬億美元大關後，巴郡現時總持倉價值466億美元。<br />\n<br />\n巴郡同時增加高盛、美國銀行、達美航空和西南航空股份。畢菲特增加21%高盛股票至持有1,320萬股，市值29.2億美元。此外，公司減持了美國航空，聯合大陸控股和富國銀行的股份，控制持股比例不超過10%。<br />\n<br />\n此外，「金融大鱷」索羅斯（George Soros）亦於第二季增加蘋果的持倉，買入5.45萬股蘋果和15.92萬股Facebook，並減持Google母公司Alphabet和亞馬遜的股份。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180815/58564991\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180815%2F58564991&d=5OJbv3QHR7oOLV3q8Uk6wywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f54b579c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180815%2F58564991&h=bd05126d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180815/58564991</a>"},{"pid":"2b10ab11b95bf8e8cd393179f5934ddcb1d27550","tid":780553,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T08:45:01.000Z","msg":"一個億股 一個萬股....蚊同牛比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c855f0136e13970879e33af9e08be8f22bfd0e","tid":780553,"uid":25434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"我啱啱都買入了5午蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}